{
  "stem": "2690.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were putting the names down of everybody that arrived, because they kept, actually, records of everybody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put our name down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I looked up, and there I see a German SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it happened to be a young man standing behind, and he motioned me to come over to him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he happened to be a friend of my brother, not knowing that he was with the SS.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew he was from German descent, but not knowing that he was that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went over to him, and he said, do like you don't know me, but I'm going to your parents' tonight.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I will keep you here, that you will not go on the transport tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the next day was already a transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every-- twice a week, they sent a thousand people away, twice a week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he said, I will keep you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People that were with us said, why don't you take your lipstick and put red spots on your door, so then they'll think she has chickenpox or some sickness?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, no, I'm not going to do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm just going to take it, and just what comes will come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I did not tell-- I wasn't allowed to tell anybody that I knew him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so, when I came back, and they were writing our names down, they said, do you know who you were speaking to?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Don't forget we traveled the whole night and I'm really a little tired.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, well, he's one of the big shots here in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, oh, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't-- I didn't know who he was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was not allowed to tell anybody that I knew him.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
